WHAT IT DOES?
=============
Android APK file, used to show essential information (clock time, miss call count and message count) on sleep screen when phone is in suspense mode.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It is a Android application project, built by Android SDK.

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
Inside Settings->Display, we will have a switch to ON/OFF Always on Display feature.
It make the screen keep on and show some system information(e.g. clock, calendar, system notification) instead of black screen in suspend stage.
The device would consumes up around 1% of battery per hour.
